attributes.title: PHOTOSHOP BATTLES FINALE
attributes.caption: WE CAN'T NOT PHOTOSHOP!
attributes.description: The time has come my friends. We are putting everything on the line for the Photoshop Battles FINALE. Thanks for this fun journey through some truly messed up creations. Please enjoy our farewell episode of the series.
